      "title": "$Backend_Developer => [PHP | Java | Laravel | Angular | Spring Boot]",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm Pedro Luque 👋  I'm a backend developer who mainly works with PHP and Laravel, as well as Python, Java, and Spring Boot. I love turning ideas into clean, functional code that not only works—but looks good under the hood.  I'm passionate about technology, programming, and photography, and I truly enjoy learning something new every day. If I don’t know how to do something, I learn it — that’s how I keep up in this fast-changing world.  Before becoming a developer, I worked in other industries, which taught me valuable soft skills that you can’t always get from a coding course: teamwork, discipline, and empathy. Today, I apply all of that to the way I code and collaborate.  I’m someone who gives 100%, never settles easily, and constantly seeks to improve every line of code. Perfectionist? Maybe. But only because I’m passionate about what I do.  If you’d like to talk about technology, exciting projects, or just share a virtual coffee ☕️ — I’d be happy to connect.",
